name: Kruse PEO Services
tag_list: peo-company-tulsa, peo-services-oklahoma, human-resources-administration, payroll-services, employee-benefits, risk-management
overview: Kruse PEO is a full-service Professional Employer Organization (PEO) providing best-in-class human resources administration, employee benefits, payroll services, workers’ compensation and risk management service and support. Our successful record in the PEO industry enables us to offer the broadest range of administrative services to Fortune 500 companies and small and medium-sized businesses in the US. Our PEO services, empowered by the most dedicated and knowledgeable staff allow employers to deal with human resources management effectively.
